---
---
<section class="cases">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="sec-head reveal"><span class="sec-index">02 / Proof</span><span class="sec-rule"></span></div>
    <h2 class="reveal">Case Studies</h2>
    <div class="case-grid">
      <!-- Case 1 -->
      <article class="case-card glow-card case-glow reveal">
        <div class="case-img" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 340 180" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <defs>
              <pattern id="d1" width="16" height="16" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
                <circle cx="1" cy="1" r="1" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.07)" />
              </pattern>
            </defs>
            <rect width="340" height="180" fill="url(#d1)" />
            <rect x="60" y="34" width="150" height="112" rx="8" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.22)" />
            <line x1="78" y1="58" x2="192" y2="58" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.30)" stroke-width="2" class="proposal-line" />
            <line x1="78" y1="76" x2="176" y2="76" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.16)" stroke-width="2" class="proposal-line" />
            <line x1="78" y1="94" x2="186" y2="94" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.16)" stroke-width="2" class="proposal-line" />
            <line x1="78" y1="112" x2="160" y2="112" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.16)" stroke-width="2" class="proposal-line" />
            <circle cx="248" cy="118" r="26" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.35)" />
            <path d="M 238 118 L 246 126 L 260 110" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.6)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <h3>Same Day Proposals for a Roofing Contractor</h3>
          <p>An agentic proposal engine reads job details from the CRM and drafts complete proposals automatically. Faster responses converted directly into more closed jobs.</p>
          <span class="stat-pill">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H8M17 7v9" /></svg>
            Two weeks to same day turnaround
          </span>
          <div class="tag-row">
            <span class="tag">Agentic Proposal Engine</span>
            <span class="tag">CRM Integration</span>
            <span class="tag">Revenue Automation</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- Case 2 -->
      <article class="case-card glow-card case-glow reveal">
        <div class="case-img" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 340 180" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect width="340" height="180" fill="url(#d1)" />
            <line x1="90" y1="90" x2="170" y2="46" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.18)" />
            <line x1="90" y1="90" x2="170" y2="134" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.18)" />
            <line x1="170" y1="46" x2="250" y2="90" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.18)" />
            <line x1="170" y1="134" x2="250" y2="90" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.18)" />
            <line x1="170" y1="46" x2="170" y2="134" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.12)" />
            <circle cx="90" cy="90" r="7" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.45)" />
            <circle cx="170" cy="46" r="7" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.45)" />
            <circle cx="170" cy="134" r="7" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.45)" />
            <circle cx="250" cy="90" r="7" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.45)" />
            <circle id="shifting-dot" cx="250" cy="90" r="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.8)" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <h3>Learning Operations on Autopilot</h3>
          <p>Learner health, mentor matching and cohort intelligence agents took over an edtech platform's operations end to end. The next cohort grew 40% with zero new hires.</p>
          <span class="stat-pill">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H8M17 7v9" /></svg>
            50% Ops Capacity Recovered
          </span>
          <div class="tag-row">
            <span class="tag">Multi Agent System</span>
            <span class="tag">Learner Intelligence</span>
            <span class="tag">Cohort Analytics</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
      <!-- Case 3 -->
      <article class="case-card glow-card case-glow reveal">
        <div class="case-img" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 340 180" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <rect width="340" height="180" fill="url(#d1)" />
            <circle cx="170" cy="90" r="4" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.8)" />
            <!-- Static Orbit Rings -->
            <circle cx="170" cy="90" r="24" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.3)" />
            <circle cx="170" cy="90" r="46" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.2)" />
            <circle cx="170" cy="90" r="68" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)" />

            <!-- Rotating Planet Groups -->
            <g class="orbit-group orbit-group-1">
              <circle cx="170" cy="66" r="3" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.7)" />
            </g>
            <g class="orbit-group orbit-group-2">
              <circle cx="212" cy="64" r="3.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" />
              <circle cx="128" cy="116" r="3.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" />
            </g>
            <g class="orbit-group orbit-group-3">
              <circle cx="196" cy="140" r="3.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)" />
              <circle cx="110" cy="58" r="3.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.4)" />
              <circle cx="236" cy="108" r="3.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.55)" />
            </g>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="case-body">
          <h3>Lead Intelligence at 5x Volume</h3>
          <p>A research and qualification system that finds, researches and qualifies prospects around the clock, cutting manual research from 15 hours a week to 2.</p>
          <span class="stat-pill">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M7 17L17 7M17 7H8M17 7v9" /></svg>
            5x Outreach Capacity
          </span>
          <div class="tag-row">
            <span class="tag">Research Automation</span>
            <span class="tag">Lead Qualification</span>
            <span class="tag">Personalized Outreach</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
